r\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Horner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Horner\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Red Bull\", \"from\": 13626, \"to\": 13634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not an instant fix, but in his third race under new principal Laurent Mekies, at home in the Netherlands, Verstappen was back on the podium.\", \"from\": 13680, \"to\": 13827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13749, \"end\": 13763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Mekies\", \"score\": 0.9999983868641998, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurent Mekies\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Mekies\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Mekies\"}, {\"begin\": 13780, \"end\": 13791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999953461156, \"rank\": 4.653887157563901e-09, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an instant fix\", \"from\": 13691, \"to\": 13705}, {\"ngram\": \"his third race\", \"from\": 13714, \"to\": 13728}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 13768, \"to\": 13772}, {\"ngram\": \"Verstappen\", \"from\": 13793, \"to\": 13803}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 13816, \"to\": 13826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He still trailed championship leader Piastri by 104 points but went on to win the next two races at Monza and Azerbaijan.\", \"from\": 13829, \"to\": 13950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13929, \"end\": 13934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monza_Circuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.135242565779966e-49, \"text\": \"Monza\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monza_Circ